        <h1 style="color: rgb(21, 22, 24);"><u>Gallantry Awards</u></h1>
        
        <p>The Garuds have actively participated in counter-terrorist operations and have received many accolades which
            include 1 Ashok Chakra, 4 Shaurya Chakras, and many Vayu Sena Medal .</p>
        <p><b><u>Shaurya Chakra</u></b>– Corporal Devendra Mehta(2018) , Corporal Nilesh (2018,posthumous) , <br>
            Sergeant Milind Kishor (2018, posthumous).</p>
